    "Furthermore, implementing rigorous cost-cutting measures and optimizing operational efficiency can generate additional funds for debt servicing.",
    "The choice of the most suitable debt management strategy depends on the specific circumstances of the business, such as its industry, financial structure, and the severity of the crisis.",
